This directory is aimed to get examples of configuration
files which are related to Linux modules development and
management.

All the examples related to a module named 'ootm'

Every example looks like:
    example with <placeholders>
    # explanation of example and placeholders

How to use it:
    1. replace <placeholders> with appropriate values
    2. copy file to the system path: ROOT/env/<dir>/ -> /<dir>/
